**Privacy Policy**

Last Updated: [Date]

This Privacy Policy describes how Rework Pvt. Ltd. ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and shares personal information when you use our [website/app/service] (the "Service"). By accessing or using the Service, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

**Information We Collect**

- **Personal Information:** We may collect information that can be used to identify you ("Personal Information"), such as your name, email address, postal address, phone number, and other similar information.

- **Usage Data:** We may collect information on how you interact with the Service, such as pages visited, features used, and other usage data.

**How We Use Your Information**

- **Provide and Improve the Service:** We use the information collected to provide, maintain, and improve the Service, as well as to personalize your experience.

- **Communicate with You:** We may use your information to send you important notices, updates, promotions, and other communications related to the Service.

**Information Sharing and Disclosure**

We do not sell or rent your Personal Information to third parties. However, we may share your information in the following circumstances:

- **Service Providers:** We may share your information with third-party service providers to help us operate, maintain, and improve the Service.

- **Legal Requirements:** We may disclose your information to comply with applicable laws, regulations, legal processes, or government requests.

**Your Choices**

You can update your Personal Information by [describing how users can update their information]. You can also opt-out of receiving promotional emails by [describing opt-out process].

**Security**

We take reasonable measures to protect your Personal Information. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure.

**Changes to this Privacy Policy**

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

**Contact Us**

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [contact email/phone number].

